headline.main: New Dive-Bomber Gives Japan Little Assistance

lead_paragraph: GUADALCANAL, Oct. 27 (Delayed) -- The Japanese have introduced a new dive-bomber into the fighting in this area, but with a remarkable lack of success.
abstract: US fliers rept new Jap dive-bomber ineffectual; down 7 out of 9 during Treasury Islands landing
